import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import Login from "../components/Login"
import Home from "../components/Home"


Vue.use(VueRouter)



const router = new VueRouter({
  routes: [
    { path: '/', redirect: '/login' },
    { path: '/login', component: Login },
    { path: '/home', component: Home },
  ]
})

export default router
